        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 px-lg-5 py-lg-5">
                      <div class="tabContent" id="0">
              <h3 class="mb-5">Consultation</h3>
              <img src="https://armesmaini.com/uploads/ourprocess/consultation1691493567.jpg" class="mb-5">
              <p class="mb-5">At Armes Maini, we understand that you need to be operational as soon as possible. We go the extra mile to understand your warehouse requirements, storage needs, space constraints and other specific requirements that you need to be considered.</p>
            </div>
                      <div class="tabContent" id="1">
              <h3 class="mb-5">Site assessment</h3>
              <img src="https://armesmaini.com/uploads/ourprocess/site_assessment1691493631.jpg" class="mb-5">
              <p class="mb-5">After the initial consultation, our in-house design engineers along with on-site surveyors&#039; inputs conduct a preliminary inspection of the site. Our on-site service team boasts years of experience, allowing them to make accurate assessments to determine the available area, ceiling height, and any potential obstacle that may impact the racking installation.</p>
            </div>
                      <div class="tabContent" id="2">
              <h3 class="mb-5">Design and engineering</h3>
              <img src="https://armesmaini.com/uploads/ourprocess/Design&amp;engineering1691493681.jpg" class="mb-5">
              <p class="mb-5">Based on your warehouse space challenges and the site assessment, our team of engineers design storage solutions tailored to your exact needs. We use advanced Solid Works 3D, PDM &amp; SAP 2000 to design detailed layouts and 3D models with a focus on operational processes and other factors such as ceiling height,load capacities, accessibility and safety regulations, etc.</p>
            </div>
                      <div class="tabContent" id="3">
              <h3 class="mb-5">Manufacturing and production</h3>
              <img src="https://armesmaini.com/uploads/ourprocess/manufacturing1691493728.jpg" class="mb-5">
              <p class="mb-5">Once the order is received and detailed layouts are approved, our skilled technicians, under the supervision of experienced engineers, commence the manufacturing process. We leverage cutting-edge technology to manufacture heavy duty racking components in alignment with the approved 3D models.</p>
            </div>
                      <div class="tabContent" id="4">
              <h3 class="mb-5">Quality assurance and testing</h3>
              <img src="https://armesmaini.com/uploads/ourprocess/quality_assurance1691493778.jpg" class="mb-5">
              <p class="mb-5">At Armes Maini, our quality control department ensures the integrity and quality of the racking systems according to stringent norms. We conduct thorough inspections and audits at every stage of production to detect any deviations from specifications.</p>
            </div>
                      <div class="tabContent" id="5">
              <h3 class="mb-5">Project planning</h3>
              <img src="https://armesmaini.com/uploads/ourprocess/project_planning1691493859.jpg" class="mb-5">
              <p class="mb-5">At Armes Maini, planning every project is the key to deliver top-of-the-segment racking and storage systems. With an aim to comprehend our clients&#039; distinct requirements and expectations, we develop a project roadmap that aligns with key parameters such as project goals, scope, timeframe, and resources. Our commitment to effective planning ensures efficient execution, on-time delivery, and customer satisfaction.</p>
            </div>
                      <div class="tabContent" id="6">
              <h3 class="mb-5">Installation audit &amp; handover</h3>
              <img src="https://armesmaini.com/uploads/ourprocess/handover1691494074.jpg" class="mb-5">
              <p class="mb-5">Armes Maini is a customer-obsessed storage and racking system manufacturing company. For us, customer relationship begins with the initial interaction and continues long after the project is completed. Throughout the entire process, our team maintains open communication ensuring that the client&#039;s expectations are met and that the systems are ready for productive use.</p>
            </div>
